{
  "stem": "7683.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and the minute we came out of this office was a truck with a German, German that came in a truck.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was bleeding, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a cut here and I was bleeding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But Selma was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somehow he didn't see me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Selma gave me quick a bandage-- ah-- a bandage-- a-- a-- a handkerchief or something like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was 5 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the group started to go back to the place where we live.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was 5 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I joined the group, and I went back to the place where we were live.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When we came there, there was different groups from all the places came, and it was a big confusion, a big-- everybody was-- you came from someplace what happened.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everybody knew already what was going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, and there was some Ukrainian came, and we killed him there on the spot, too, because-- and there was [? going around ?] in the camp, [? going around ?] there was an hour was going.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The electricity was cut off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The telephone was cut off because they're afraid maybe somebody would come and communicate outside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- so when we came back, there was 5 o'clock, and we all start to running in all directions.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of people run in the mines, got killed there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of people went to the front gate and got killed there, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was-- there was some shooting because some of the Jews had an access to the warehouse from ammunition.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they got some guns and some guns and revolvers and things like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was a lot of shooting going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Germans start some-- whoever is still left was afraid, I guess.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I see still Frenzel.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
